net.explorviz.landscape.repository.persistence.mongo

Class MongoLandscapeRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.explorviz.landscape.repository.persistence.mongo.MongoLandscapeRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LandscapeRepository<net.explorviz.shared.landscape.model.landscape.Landscape>

    public class MongoLandscapeRepository
extends java.lang.Object
implements LandscapeRepository<net.explorviz.shared.landscape.model.landscape.Landscape>
    Stores and retrieves landscapes from a mongodb, which is given in the explorviz.properties resource.

    This repository will return all requested landscapes as actual java objects. Since landscapes are stored in json api format, this requires costy deserialization. If you don't need the actual object but rather just their strin representation, use MongoLandscapeJsonApiRepository

    This class is just a decorator for MongoLandscapeJsonApiRepository which deserializes the retrieved objects.
